How cheap, a Maximal lying about a battle!

::DeathScythe::

DeathScythe scans the area he had been flying through. He knew there had to 
be bots somewhere, and when he met them, they would probably die. Now he just 
had to find the bots.

He was flying over a mountain range, his scanners working hard to detect any 
bots.
